    "As noted by Gibson (2017), triangulation refines the research by removing biases so that the validity and credibility of the studies can be enhanced substantially.",
    "This study was carried out at a private university located in Erbil, Iraq.",
    "The participants were selected via cluster sampling among the students who enrolled in the Foundation English course during the 2023-2024 Academic Year.",
    "Fifty students, 22 male and 28 female, were picked from the population, and their ages ranged from 17 to 24.",
    "The Foundation English course has been offered for students whose levels are not as satisfactory as others based on the proficiency exam results conducted by the university."
  ],
